1 (iv) Minutes of regular, emergency, and special
2 meetings of the school district board of directors that shall be posted no
3 later than twenty-four (24) hours following the approval of the minutes at a
4 regular, emergency, or special meeting of the school district board of
5 directors;
6 (v) The school district budget for the ensuing year,
